reviewText:
try this blade before you give up all the chrome ie de safety razor :)
I tried with merkur and feather blade and almost gave up on de but then I tried wilkinson and what a difference. this blade is even better than Mach 3.! I ordered 100 after trying sample pack.! just 20c a piece now. and it lasts about same as mach3 razor costing much much more.!
and what's matter with chrome? well we all know ready made razor is mostly plastic. and I hate plastics. de razors are mostly chrome and I love shiny chromes
